  "text": "The largest logistics union in the country is threatening a nationwide walkout. Their demand is simple: freeze warehouse automation for eighteen months or they strike. Members already lost eleven thousand jobs to sorting robots this year. Half of next quarter's automation savings were supposed to come from those warehouses.",
